sentences: Lil' Wil (born Wil Martin, March 25, 1987) is an American rapper.
In late 2007, he released the single "My Dougie", which charted on four Billboard singles charts.
It was the lead-off single to his debut album Dolla$, TX, which was released in June 2008 by Asylum Records executive producer Pimp-n-Keys Ent and charted at #3 on Billboard's Top Heatseekers chart.
